{"tid":383630,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"原來銀行做COUNTER有請PART TIME","createTime":"2017-09-01T15:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T10:25:00.000Z","uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4536203537c14db4e89aae4bf3f0bac8536207f7","tid":383630,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"前幾日去入數<br />\n聊個死o靚仔teller仔傾計<br />\n點知佢話自己黎緊就黎開學無得成日番工<br />\n人工係咪好撚高?<br />\n我諗銀行出手都唔會低得去邊 起碼都有80掛<br />\n當年我番學個陣都係做賣衫仔 得45蚊一粒鐘咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0804fa8f32b7ac83b29e733730635020020a3065","tid":383630,"uid":21247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"得五十幾喳"},{"pid":"7a462e39389f13681ee7a57d65d9586a26ae3444","tid":383630,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得五十幾喳</blockquote><br />\n咁cheap? 仲做係咩心態"},{"pid":"3de4fb7748e3bd9b2660480350162451fce22d8d","tid":383630,"uid":22889,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得五十幾喳</blockquote><br />\n咁cheap? 仲做係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n寫落cv好睇囉<br />\n唔通寫賣衫咩"},{"pid":"05d82dd54606f116aff1205e0b74d95a24cd9a95","tid":383630,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得五十幾喳</blockquote><br />\n咁cheap? 仲做係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n寫落cv好睇囉<br />\n唔通寫賣衫咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f45caadb13339c7fd12988db17344ecc6507a88","tid":383630,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得五十幾喳</blockquote><br />\n咁cheap? 仲做係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n寫落cv好睇囉<br />\n唔通寫賣衫咩</blockquote><br />\n正解"},{"pid":"77050fb262ab81be9755cf1dc6dc7b5c77381b72","tid":383630,"uid":138552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T18:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得五十幾喳</blockquote><br />\n咁cheap? 仲做係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n寫落cv好睇囉<br />\n唔通寫賣衫咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8ca3c6c84c7a245e40b7eeac8225df4c20392a","tid":383630,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T18:41:15.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"71f69a3eb0db8c6c1cfa538778b8d3f210d02a32","tid":383630,"uid":84871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T01:09:27.000Z","msg":"五十五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就來做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a824901f353170bdf44adab466a561ed030c8d7d","tid":383630,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得五十幾喳</blockquote><br />\n咁cheap? 仲做係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n寫落cv好睇囉<br />\n唔通寫賣衫咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畢業之後咪又係繼續做counter仔<br />\n袋同d新人一樣既人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097b74f6ab4233baaa62197f11587d54baa629bf","tid":383630,"uid":7994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五十五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就來做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一講呢個價就知係邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係新手價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}